<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.6">
<l>ālat tilaiyā ṉaravi ṉaṇaimēlāṉ</l>
<l>nīlak kaṭaluḷ neṭuṅkālam kaṇvaḷarntāṉ</l>
<l>pālap pirāyattē pārttark karuḷceyta</l>
<l>kōlap pirāṉukkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">kuṭantaik kiṭantārkkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff for the beautiful Lord</l>
<l>who granted grace to Pārtha at a young age,</l>
<l rend="indent">He who [sleeps] on a banyan leaf and on a serpent bed,</l>
<l rend="indent">He who rests a long time in the blue sea.</l>
<l>Bring a staff for the one who sleeps in Kuṭantai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
